snippet.title: Aleph One: Marathon Open Source
snippet.description: Aleph One is the open source continuation of Bungie's Marathon 2 FPS game engine. Aleph One plays Marathon, Marathon 2, Marathon Infinity, and 3rd-party content on a wide array of platforms, with (optional) OpenGL rendering, Internet play, Lua scripting, and more.

snippet.title: Marathon - GUI Acceptance Test Runner
snippet.description: Marathon runs gui based acceptance tests against Java/Swing applications. Marathon provides an integrated environment for test script creation and execution. Currently, Marathon supports Jython and JRuby script models for recording the test scripts.
